MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 351

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE KAPATAGAN BARANGAY HIGH SCHOOL CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN KAPATAGAN, LAAK, DAVAO PROVINCE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, JOSEPH EJERCITO ESTRADA, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale, entry, disposition or settlement and reserve for school site purposes of the Kapatagan Barangay High School, under the administration of the Department of Education, Culture and Sports, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in Barangay Kapatagan, Municipality of Laak, Province of Davao, Island of Mindanao, which are more particularly described as follows:

Lot No. 968, Cad-790-D (Ap-112321-000622)

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 968, Cad-790-D, (Ap-112321-000622), situated in Kapatagan, Municipality of Laak, Province of Davao, Island of Mindanao.

Bounded on the NE., along line 4-5 by Road; SE., along line 5-1 by Lot 969; along line 1-2 by Lot 970 both by Cad-970-D; SW., along line 2-3 by Road and NW; along line 3-4 by Lot 1714, Cad-970-D (Ap-112321-000622)

Beginning from point marked “1” on plan, being S., 28-32’E., 4,210.41 m. from BLLM No. 1, Cad-790-D, thence:

97.16 m. to point 2;

71.46 m. to point 3;

131.76 m. to point 4;

71.75 m. to point 5;

55.00 m. to point 1;

point of beginning, containing an area of TEN THOUSAND TWO (10,002) square meter, more or less. All corners are PS Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cm. Bearings Grid. Date of original survey, April 15, 1992 to May 29, 1992; Date prepared July 26, 1993, by Geodetic III Engineer Victor Londeta, approved on July 30, 1993.

Lot No. 1714, Cad-790-D (Ap-112321-000622)

A PARCEL OF LAND, Lot 1714, Cad-790-D, situated in Kapatagan, Municipality of Laak, Province of Davao, Island of Mindanao.

Bounded on the NE., along line 1-2 by Road; SE., along line 2-3 by Lot 968, Cad-790-D (AP-112321-000622); SW., along line 3-4 by Road; NW., along line 4-1 by Lot 962, Cad-790-D, thence:

Beginning from point marked “1” on plan, being S., 27-40’E., 4022.63 m. from BLLM No. 1, Cad-790-D, thence:

60.72 m. to point 2;

131.76 m. to point 3;

66.67 m. to point 4;

134.95 m. to point 1;

point of beginning, containing an area of EIGHT THOUSAND FOUR HUNDRED EIGHTY FIVE (8,485) square meters, more or less. All corners are “PS” Cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 60 m. Bearings Grid. Date of Original Survey, April 15, 1992 to May 29, 1992; Date prepared, July 26, 1993, by Geodetic Engineer III, Victor P. Landeta, approved on July 30, 1993.

The tracts of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease, or other disposition until again declared alienable by proclamation of the President.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 9 Th day of August, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand.

(Sgd.) JOSEPH EJERCITO ESTRADA

By the President: (Sgd.) RONALDO B. ZAMORA Executive Secretary

